<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kumsawt Hinna Lultak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kumsawt hinna lultak ka nei tai,
 Zie khawvel zawha ngamna chu!
 Lal Isu leh a nasep haw gingin,
 Zo in ka ngam suol thihna gallien.

[V2]
 Zie hi ahi khawvel zawha ngamna chu, I ginnau hi; (2)
 Aw thihna khawia na gu chu ?
 Aw than khawia na zawhna chu?
 Hin kiem loin kum sawt in leng tang ka,
 Hallelujah Zotu Lalpa chu pakchang ka.

[V3]
 2. Tuhin gitloh gal hung lien mahleh,
 Zo ing ka Lal Krista zalin;
 Pathien thu hing chemzam leh ginna phaw,
 Mangin zo ingka gitloh gallien,

[V4]
 3. Vaihawmna hung tung ding lau puong ka,
 Thiemchan lawkna ka neih ziekin,
 Kuo a ka Lalpa ma a ei hek ding?
 Keia a hi Amah a ka hi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>319</hymn_number>
</song>